The '''2015 Egypt bus accident''' occurred on 21 March 2015 when a [[bus]] fell off a bridge near [[Giza]] in [[Egypt]]. It plunged into a canal, killing at least 35, many of whom worked for a private [[construction]] company.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.news.com.au/world/breaking-news/egyptian-bus-accident-kills-at-least-35/story-e6frfkui-1227272929634|title=Egyptian bus accident kills at least 35|work=NewsComAu}}</ref>
