==Voting== ===Televoting=== After the juries had selected 5 songs for a "super final", it was revealed that the TV viewers would choose the winner by regional [[televoting]]. However, the voting became a bit repetitive, and televoting was not re-introduced until [[Melodifestivalen 1999|six years later]] when it was combined with regional juries.
