{{more references|date=July 2018}}[[File:UAE Awafi Festival3.jpg|thumb|Sand dune adventure in Awafi]] [[File:UAE Awafi Festival2.jpg|thumb|Sand duning in Awafi]]
The '''UAE Awafi Festival''' is an annual festival in the [[United Arab Emirates]]. It is held in the spring. It celebrates the Emirates' ethnic and cultural heritage through outdoor sporting events, theater performances and cultural displays. The festival includes competitions in which participants scale sand dunes in various vehicles.<ref>{{cite news|title=YouTube Videos of Awafi Festival RAK|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s4r_xOkYRG8}}</ref> The event is held in the Awafi area (known for its red sand dunes) in [[Ras al-Khaimah]], [[United Arab Emirates]] (UAE).<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.khaleejtimes.com/nation/ras-al-khaimah/ras-al-khaimah-concludes-awafi-festival|title=Ras Al Khaimah concludes Awafi festival|website=www.khaleejtimes.com|access-date=2018-08-03}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.rakftz.com/kaytoob/nl/ArticleID/11029/Awafi-Festival-Sets-off-Celebrations-in-RAK|title=Awafi Festival Sets off Celebrations in RAK|last=Kaytoob|work=Kaytoob|access-date=2018-08-03|language=en-US}}</ref>
The festival is open to the public. Attendees usually arrive in off-road vehicles.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://gulfnews.com/news/uae/culture/visitors-flock-to-awafi-festival-1.1948650|title=Visitors flock to Awafi Festival|last=Report|first=Staff|date=2016-12-19|work=GulfNews|access-date=2018-08-10}}</ref>
The festival includes a Heritage Village show, local arts and crafts exhibitions, a bazaar, children's play area, clinics and a police aid.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.hoteliermiddleeast.com/29054-ras-al-khaimah-opens-awafi-festival/|title=Ras Al Khaimah opens Awafi Festival {{!}} HotelierMiddleEast.com|last=Thompson|first=David|work=HotelierMiddleEast.com|access-date=2018-08-10}}</ref>. Food outlets, internet cafÃ©s and coffee shops are available. The car and dune [[bike racing]] competitions are held in December or January.<ref>{{cite news| title=Awafi Festival Begins in RAK Today|url=http://www.khaleejtimes.com/darticlen.asp?xfile=data/theuae/2010/January/theuae_January845.xml&section=theuae |accessdate=6 September 2010 | newspaper= [[Khaleej Times]] |date=29 January 2010}}</ref>
==Location== The festival is located in the Ras al-Khaimah desert. This desert is home to many towering sand dunes and harbors rough terrain. The area covers 500 acres.
